        "| 9 | Dynamical Systems and Markov Chains | linear iteration, stochastic matrices, Perron-Frobenius | [chapter-09](chapters/chapter-09-dynamical-systems-markov-chains-perron-frobenius.qmd) | [lab-09](labs/lab-09-dynamical-systems-markov-chains.qmd) |\n",
